extendedInfo.description: Christian Financial Credit Union is a full service financial institution located in Michigan. You can also use the map feature to locate us, see our hours, contact us to request additional information, review our products and services, inquire about credit union membership and more!

reviews.title: Lg Motion 4g
reviews.comment: This app got ALOT BETTER. It still needs a little work!! I can actually log in, and view my accounts in a larger window!! However I would like to see more payment options and be able to view my credit card info.

reviews.comment: App did work great. I loved it, made checking an transferring money very easy.. But now the last 2 weeks or so I can\'t even open the app I have to go to the full website and check everything that way.. So I\'m very disappointed. I have uninstalled it 3 different times, an I still get nothing.. hope they fix it soon.. it made my life a lot easier..   So until its fix only 1 star.. sorry!!!!!
